{"tid":1702433,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益－屎魔法Roadblock大法","createTime":"2019-11-09T16:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T17:05:26.000Z","uid":69416,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0d73a45ba8ffd87fbb98aa82a810ef7e2704548b","tid":1702433,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:38:45.000Z","msg":"突發奇想<br />\n其實屎魔法係咪應該用係路障上面<br />\n小弟發夢幾次都見過<br />\n路障過一段時間就會被部份私家車司機落車搬走<br />\n除此之外搬走roadblock既多數都係D狗<br />\n淋屎水一黎D<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">私家車司機好大機會唔撚敢掂</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">二黎D狗搬撚完要臭足幾尻個鐘</span></strong><br />\n分分鐘換更下手未黎得切洗就要著果件咁既閪屌野<br />\nRoadblock威嚇力大增　手足們有無意見"},{"pid":"c5b4e487eac59824b20a6f17fed160b488264ae6","tid":1702433,"uid":69416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:39:06.000Z","msg":"即係直接就咁淋上E Roadblock上面"},{"pid":"324bf459575b0b6bfdf96816c3aed068f2d8c19c","tid":1702433,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:39:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3cf81305106a1e4aaca0cf4c9b1ed3cf5c6ad6db","tid":1702433,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:39:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5fc13a801c872f6436b7e29c1fa3e185a3e246d5","tid":1702433,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:40:11.000Z","msg":"其實未必要去到屎<br />\n就咁淋尿咁由佢發酵都會幾撚臭下"},{"pid":"ae3ec7e244c0fe299a3db78a43c059d90a45aad9","tid":1702433,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:40:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"569409a37f468a9d79ed2cd41b2e66a594b436cd","tid":1702433,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:40:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"66b92e1017ee8d225ed37f165c2b2d2ba532132b","tid":1702433,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:40:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"13c7e01dedca56aa337dfff4414f9cb3beba4dc6","tid":170243